name: Selfportrait on the movieset Starship Troopers 1997
description: Yes, this is me working as extra and stander on that movieset. For the young ones, Starship Troopers is a 1997 American military science fiction action film directed by Paul Verhoeven and written by Edward Neumeier, based on Robert A. Heinlein's 1959 novel of the same name.
